plar", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Poplar standard", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271047/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271110/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1935", "dates": ["[1935 TO 1940]"], "description": ["Weekly -v. 5, no. 34 (Jan. 11, 1940). Merged with: Wolf Point herald, to form: Herald-news (Wolf Point, Mont.). Volume Five, Number 33 (January 4, 1940); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 16, 2024). Volume Five, Number 34 (January 11, 1940) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 16, 2024). Wolf Point herald Herald-news (Wolf Point, Mont.) (DLC) 2024271111"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:15.756Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271110/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["montana", "wolf point", "united states", "roosevelt"], "number": ["1434062239", "online resource", "2997-8556", "2024271111", "2024271110", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "roosevelt county news (wolf point, roosevelt county, montana) 1935-1940 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 24.722351, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["montana", "wolf point", "united states", "roosevelt"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:57.142Z", "title": "Roosevelt County news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271110/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271111/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1940", "dates": ["[1940 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. XXVII, no. 51 (January 18, 1940). Briefly carries numbering of both the Wolf Point herald and the Roosevel County news; continues numbering of the Wolf Point herald. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Formed by the union of: Wolf Point herald, and: Roosevelt County news. Vol. XXVII, No. 51 (January 18, 1940); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 16, 2024). Vol. 42, No. 49 (December 15, 1955) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 16, 2024)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:15.756Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271111/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["montana", "wolf point", "united states", "roosevelt"], "number": ["1434062668", "2997-8572", "online resource", "2024271110", "2024271111", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the herald-news (wolf point, roosevelt county, montana) 1940-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 24.722351, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "montana", "wolf point (mont.)", "roosevelt", "wolf point", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:57.142Z", "title": "The herald-news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271111/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271284/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1913", "dates": ["[1913 TO 1940]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1913; ceased v. 27, no. 50 (Jan. 10, 1940). Merged with: Roosevelt County news, to form: Herald-news (Wolf Point, Mont.). Description based on: Volume VII. No. 45. (Janaury 1, 1920); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 21, 2020). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XX, Number Forty-Seven (December 30, 1932) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 21, 2020). R